{"tid":1104313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上水兩男童玩gas罐搶火燒傷 兩男女涉虐兒被捕","createTime":"2019-04-13T05:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T05:55:40.000Z","uid":3090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c31177b12e67fa21c75c8e8c5be23b589a6055e8","tid":1104313,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T05:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rf2qtTm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRf2qtTm.png&h=1c1c132f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DcRF2dn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDcRF2dn.png&h=855a55a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n楊父指受傷的兒子無大礙，他又否認自己被捕。周鴻熙攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eSgbprT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeSgbprT.png&h=391f3fb4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZSTdCMU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZSTdCMU.png&h=f1b9d7e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VMmyCMV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVMmyCMV.png&h=f7c06e1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩名男童在村屋內玩小型石油氣罐時搶火被燒傷。<br />\n<br />\n【周六12:25】今晨《蘋果》到丙崗村楊童家了解事件，發現家門前有燒過的紙張，楊父指「個仔玩火燒着咗嘢」，問到楊童燒傷情況，楊父說「佢冇嘢，挨親吓，佢平時冇玩火。」另一名受傷姓陳男童，是楊在補習社的同學。楊父說昨日事發時他不在家，「我知差人嚟過，送咗佢（兒子）入醫院，差人冇拉我。」說罷表示出門探望在醫院的兒子。<br />\n<br />\n上水發生男童燒傷意外，傍晚6時許，一名9歲姓楊男童與同齡姓陳男友人，於丙崗村一間鐵皮屋玩打邊爐用的小型石油氣罐，其間有人點火，石油氣罐隨即搶火，兩名男童走避不及，同樣頭及手腳被燒傷，他們痛極呼叫，鄰居聞言趕至協助報案。<br />\n<br />\n救護員接報到場，將兩名男童送往沙田威爾斯醫院治理。警方調查後，以涉嫌對所看管兒童或少年人虐待或忽略被捕，，拘捕楊的54歲父親、及陳的55歲祖母。"},{"pid":"cb518f77c91f29672ccedb4b9771813426f24ab8","tid":1104313,"uid":59567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T05:13:51.000Z","msg":"窮人生仔系列"},{"pid":"5cbddbdbd4df618cfd0029881ab2309b90a7e069","tid":1104313,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cb518f77c91f29672ccedb4b9771813426f24ab8","tid":1104313,"uid":59567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T05:13:51.000Z","msg":"窮人生仔系列"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T05:16:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f924d8ac624b6312d6bde3aa83b9ffee734963","tid":1104313,"uid":159881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T05:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c4828bc2562600d3147f77f59df4066dce69e2","tid":1104313,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T05:32:11.000Z","msg":"個細路童年應該幾開心"},{"pid":"0fbd6abb4d4808f06b2200afddf3152552777996","tid":1104313,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T05:55:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我細個都成日玩火<br />\n智商正常啲都識醒水唔會燒親<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：sci phd</span>"}]}